    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1878. 另一个蒸汽朋克现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >洪水吞噬了一切。世界变成了一望无际的海洋。幸存者们学会了建造移动岛屿 - “Isla Muvimi”，用于贸易和通讯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras/7da8df52d7cc55c1296f73b4bc0eff0a.poster.avif?t=1771528343\" width=1170 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras/7da8df52d7cc55c1296f73b4bc0eff0a.webm?t=1771528343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras/7da8df52d7cc55c1296f73b4bc0eff0a.mp4?t=1771528343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您必须穿越茫茫大海，寻找神话中的大陆。玩家等待着海战和空战、水下深处的奥秘和寻找盟友，以便在这个艰难的世界中生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造并发展您的移动岛屿 - “Isla Muvimi”，带它踏上无尽的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras/d5d8511ea026d11780cf7aa66a817ca8.avif?t=1771528343\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras_big/d5d8511ea026d11780cf7aa66a817ca8.avif?t=1771528343 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建设和管理您的浮动基地岛。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制你的战斗炮塔、飞机和潜水艇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在《海行者传奇》的世界中探索广阔的海洋，与敌人战斗，寻找惊人的秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏情节引人入胜，灵感来自凯文-科斯特纳主演的电影《水世界》。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着玩家经验的积累，主角会变得越来越强大和聪明。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras/eebf77df69b0b334ed890fae980bfff1.poster.avif?t=1771528343\" width=800 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras/eebf77df69b0b334ed890fae980bfff1.webm?t=1771528343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169360/extras/eebf77df69b0b334ed890fae980bfff1.mp4?t=1771528343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
